channel.title: ZodiacsReign Forever V.11 Pack [Re-Release] [11,000 Downloads In Series]
channel.description:
[ul][list][list][list][list][center][Img]http://i44.tinypic.com/9ithdl.png[/img][/center] [center] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/vgso5v.png[/img] [size=24pt]Officially 11,000 Downloads[/size] [size=20pt][b][/size][/center] [center][b][i]What is ZodiacsReign?[/i] [b][font=Verdana]ZodiacsReign is a RSPS helper containing mostly required programs and files to make your RSPS coding and playing more proficient and easy, Zodiacsreign has been around for almost 2 years and I've been updating for a very long time. In "ZodiacsReign Packages" you will find Tools, Id List , Essentials to make your private server experience a better one.[/b][/center] [color=maroon] [center][b][i] [color=blue]This is the FINAL folder pack, definitely the final folder pack. I'm not making anymore folder packs, so those of you that love folder packs, say goodbye to folder packs. I won't release another one of these for a very long time.
[size=12pt]Also, Seriously guys, if you're going to release a pack like I do, please don't base it on mines and call it your pack.[/size]
[b] [size=14pt]Make sure to download ZodiacsReign [i]Lite[/i] if the file is too big[/b] http://www.mediafire.com/?dyjmtmmjkmf
[/b][/center]
[center] [size=15pt]Servers, Clients, Call it boring. What about Packs? Make one today! [/size]
[Center][size=20pt]Download Link~[/size] [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/zodiacsreign][IMG]http://i33.tinypic.com/slrwo0.png[/img][/URL] [b]19MB[/b]
Last Month [img]http://i27.tinypic.com/erzxw2.jpg[/img] http://i38.tinypic.com/2u5b76t.png This Month [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/2u5b76t.png[/img]
[img]http://www.mediafire.com/images/v4images/logo.gif[/img]
[/center]
[center] [b]What's new? 603 Item List 603 Npc List 603 Object List Animation Pack Runescape INT Editor Decompiler New Model Grabber All-In-On Renamer Item Statter - Change Stats in an Instant New Price Checker And more. [/b]
[Center][i][size=11pt][b]Features[/b][/center] [center] [b][size=12pt]317 List[/b] [list] [color=orange][list][li]317 Item List[/li][/list] [list][li]317 NPC List[/li] [li]317 Interface List[/li] [li]317 Graphics List[/li] [li]317 Object List[/li] [li]317 Emote List [/li] [li]317 Coordinate List [/li] [li]317 Animation List [/li] [li]And More[/li][/list]
[b][size=12pt][color=green]508 List[/b] [list][li]508 Interface List[/li] [li]508 NPC List [/li] [li]508 Object List[/li] [li]508 Item List[/li] [li]508 Graphics List[/li] [li]508 Hair & Clothes Color List[/li] [li]508 Emotes List[/li] [li]508 Sounds List [/li][/list]
[b][size=12pt][color=blue]Tools[/b] [list][li]Eleclions Server Rebooter[/li] [li]Meiscooldudes Shopmaker & Server Runetime Manager[/li] [li]Hypercam Set-Up[/li] [li]Basic Command Generator[/li] [li]Voule's Auto-Restarter[/li] [li]Voule's Command Generator [/li] [li]Voule's Auto-spawn Generator[/li] [li]Backup Tool[/li] [li]Character Editor[/li] [li]Runescape Windows Client[/li] [li]WinterLove Server[/li] [li]Brand new Shop-Maker[/li] [li]Sprite-Maker[/li] [li]Moparscape Client[/li] [li]Server Item Clearer[/li] [li]525 Item List[/li] [li]Auto-typer & Auto-clicker[/li] [li]And More[/li] [li]More tools then before![/li] [/list]
[b][size=14pt]Picture[/size][/b] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/2ivo5md.jpg[/img] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/20ayza0.jpg[/img][/center]
[Center]
[size=12pt][b]Virus Scan(s)[/b][/size] [img]http://i41.tinypic.com/20jfdhs.jpg[/img] [img]http://i26.tinypic.com/331hyf6.png[/img]
[size=23pt]Credits[/size] [b]I'd like to thank all of those that aided me through these five years of private servers. [b][size=8pt][color=green] Cocoa - For his support Hidendra - For his support The Soul - For his support Galkon - For his support Jagex LTD - RuneScape SilabSoft - Silabsoft Client L E G A C Y "Justin" - For reminding me that I'm powerhungry Jeremy Yak - Tools Autoc4st - For his support Jon of Hollow-Point - Have to love his suggestions. Voule - Tools Meiscooldudes - Tools Zee Best - 525 List GalkonsPride Community BytyIsle Community Emps-Scape Community Hollow-Point & Eternal-Reign Community ForeverNow Community Moparscape Community R-S Community RuneLimited Community Emps-Scape Community Affliction Community Enkrona/RuneFusion Community Blaze-Scape Community Pur3z-Scape Community PloxageScape Community Apple for making iTunes Microsoft for making Windows Apple for making iPhones [Img]http://i29.tinypic.com/2u6mw02.png[/img][center]
[center][size=18pt]Quotes[/size] [b]Lin From Moparscape[/b] : Nice job. Why don't you work on a server though? The packages out there aren't going to get any better than this to be honest.
[b]Galkon, Mod of R-S [/b] : Great job, I'll definitely use tools in this.
[b] Hidendra, Mopar Vet[/b] : DON'T WORRY THERE'S NO VIRUSES EVERYONE, SO DON'T ASK FOR TWO FUCKING VIRUS SCANS or i will kill you
[b]Cocoa, Blaze-Scape Creator[/b] : I already have this one on my computer, This is the best pack yet imo.
[center][i]ZodiacsReign 11.0 was made by Z 0 D I A C of Moparscape/R-S Forums & Released on July 15,2010 This pack was released for learning purposes only, Runescape was made by Jagex[/i][/center]
